    CellLabeler-class

    Each CellLabeler object has a number of slots which store information. Key slots to access are listed below.

    show(<CellLabeler>)

    Overview of a Celllabeler object

    CellLabeler.plot()

    Plot gene score for clusters regarding each possible cell types.

    CombinePValues()

    Cauchy combination rules

    ComputeGeneScore()

    Compute gene score based on combined pvalue and gene expression percents.

    ComputePCT()

    Compute gene expression percent of single-cell RNA data.

    ComputePrediction()

    Compute gene score and perform predictions.

    CreateCellLabelerObject()

    Create the CellLabeler object with filtering step

    FindAllUniqueMarkers()

    Fitting the firth logistic regression model to perform unique marker gene analysis for clustered scRNA-seq data

    RegressOutMatrix()

    Regress out the sample batch effects

    allGenes()

    Collect all genes in the analysis,

    Fitting the constrained spline model to perform temporal differential expression analysis for time course scRNA-seq data

    Permutation of two of all categories
